        "new_rules_in_this_unit": [
            "Use two-way prepositions (an, auf, hinter, in, neben, über, unter, vor, zwischen) with the dative case to describe where something is located (Wo?).",
            "Use stehen, liegen, hängen, and sitzen with dative two-way prepositions to describe the position of objects: stehen for objects with a base, liegen for flat/baseless objects, hängen for hanging objects, sitzen for seated things."
        ],
